        <body>
            <div type="witness" subtype="poem" met="-+|-+|-+|-+" rhyme="aa">
                <head type="title"><hi rend="caps">CHIAVENNA</hi><ref type="gloss_textual" target="oh_softly_blew_the_morning_breeze_poem_glosses_textual.php#CHIAVENNATITLE" /></head>
                <lg type="stanza" n="1">
                    <l>O<hi rend="smallcaps">H</hi>, softly blew the mounting breeze<ref type="gloss_textual" target="oh_softly_blew_the_morning_breeze_poem_glosses_textual.php#MOUNTINGBREEZE" /></l>
                    <l>Through <placeName corresp="#CHIAVENNA">Chiavenna</placeName>&#x02BC;s <name type="botanical" corresp="#MYRTLE">myrtle trees</name>,</l>
                <l>And o&#x02BC;er the green hills&#x02BC; viny spread,</l> 
                <l>That rose in many a rounded head</l>
                <l>Beneath the Alpine rocks of red.</l>
                    <l>And the fresh snow had fall&#x02BC;n that night,</l> 
                <l>And sprinkled with its mantle white</l>
                <l>The mountain amphitheatre</l>
                    <l>That rose around us far and near,<ref type="gloss_contextual" target="oh_softly_blew_the_morning_breeze_poem_glosses_contextual.php#MOUNTAINAMPHITHEATRE"/></l>
                <l>Though in such far confusion hurled</l>
                <l>They looked to rule o&#x02BC;er all the world;</l> 
                <l>And the white clouds seemed to immerse</l>
                <l>Another ruined universe.</l>
                </lg>
            </div>
